{"title":"The $300 DJI Mini SE drone launches with fully stabilized, gimbal-mounted 2.7K camera","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/13/the-300-dji-mini-se-drone-launches-with-fully-stabilized-gimbal-mounted-2-7k-camera/","date":1628865300000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>OK, so it’s not 4K. But it’s $300, which is less than a GoPro HERO9…and it flies. Not only that, but the new DJI Mini SE gets many of their best automated flight patterns, a 3-axis motorized gimbal, and an incredible 4km range with the remote control. Did we mention it’s just $300?</p><p>If you’re looking for a pocket-sized drone that weighs just 249g and has 30 minutes of flight time, here’s everything you need to know about DJI’s most affordable consumer drone yet…</p><h2>DJI Mini SE drone specs &amp; details</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"dji mini se drone in the palm of a hand\" width=\"1599\" height=\"1067\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1599w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-1536x1025.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-1068x713.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-629x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1599px) 100vw, 1599px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.42248489701920056\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1599w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-1536x1025.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-1068x713.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101018/dji-mini-se-drone-closeup-629x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 629w\"></a></p><p>In addition to shooting 2.7K stabilized video, some of the standout features of the new Mini SE include:</p><ul><li>12MP photos</li><li>GPS-enabled precision hovering</li><li>Up to 30 minutes flight time</li><li>Dronie, Rocket, Circle, and Helix QuickShot modes</li><li>Cinema control mode</li></ul><p>Combined, these features mean you can quickly capture professional looking shots thanks to the pre-programmed QuickShot modes with plenty of air time to try them all.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller.jpg\" alt=\"dji mini se remote control with smartphone attachment\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1043\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-297x207.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-800x556.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-120x83.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-768x534.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-696x484.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-1068x743.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-604x420.jpg 604w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-100x70.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-297x207.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-800x556.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-120x83.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-768x534.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-696x484.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-1068x743.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-604x420.jpg 604w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101038/dji-mini-se-drone-remote-controller-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>For those of us who like to direct our own shots, or need to follow a moving subject, Cinema Mode slows down flight controls for more stable, less jerky flight motions. We’ve played around with this on our Mini 2 and found that it definitely helps smooth turns and rotations, yielding better footage.</p><p>Unfortunately, DJI doesn’t have a sizzle reel out for this model yet, but you can <a href=\"https://www.dji.com/mini-se/video\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">see demos of their different features</a> on their website.</p><p>For this price, you aren’t getting the proximity sensors or subject follow tracking features like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/04/16/dji-air-2s-drone-adds-better-camera-obstacle-avoidance/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DJI Air 2S</a> ($999 to $1,299). And the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/11/04/dji-mavic-mini-2-brings-intelligent-4k-features-to-its-pocket-sized-drone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DJI Mini 2</a> ($449 to $599) has a better 4K camera and longer 10km transmission range (with remote control).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package.jpg\" alt=\"dji mini se drone box contents show what is included\" width=\"1500\" height=\"802\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-297x159.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-800x428.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-768x411.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-696x372.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-1068x571.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-786x420.jpg 786w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-297x159.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-800x428.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-768x411.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-696x372.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-1068x571.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/13101029/dji-mini-se-drone-fly-more-combo-package-786x420.jpg 786w\"></a></p><p>It’s worth pointing out that the Mini SE does include a remote control with Smartphone attachment. But, it has fewer features and controls on it than those included with their higher-end drones, relying more heavily on the Fly DJI app’s settings on your smartphone to tweak the settings and modes.</p><p>Retail is $299 for the drone, which includes one battery, the remote control, accessory cables, and a full-coverage propeller shield, making it safe(r) to fly indoors and around small children. There’s no Fly More combo available yet, but it uses the same batteries (and many of the same accessories) as the Mini 2, just <a href=\"https://www.dji.com/mini-se/faq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">check DJI’s FAQ page</a> for exact cross-compatibility.</p><p>The DJI Mini SE launched in several other countries over the past few weeks, but is now available in the USA. As of this post going live, it’s not even listed on DJI’s own online store, but you can get it through <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B098XMSQ3P/?tag=20br-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Amazon</a> and <a href=\"https://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/1651775-REG/dji_cp_ma_00000324_01_mini_se.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BH Photo</a>.</p></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4c4a6a048395098c7a4b7f4107f1d94b7d204e32b5627eaa28a55d132a77f260","category":"Cycling"}